criterion_text: Written informed parent consent and child assent
Signed IRB approved, written informed consent.
Informed consent signed by the subject.
Informed and written consent for enrollment in study
Written and voluntary informed consent understood, signed and dated.
Written informed consent from a parent/legal guardian
Signed informed consent of study participation
Written informed consent by patient or legal authorized representative
Written and informed consent from patient or a legally acceptable representative.
Written informed consent and/or signed assent line from patient, parent or guardian
Patient has voluntarily agreed to participate by giving written informed consent
